    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-07-05T02:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-07-05T02:00:00-05:00" n="818"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d818">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">124.93/7–549: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister-Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clark</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Canton</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-07-05T15:00:00+08:00"
                            >July 5, 1949—3 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received July 5—10:15 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cantel 688. Informal survey here indicates practically all nations represented
                    here plan send mission Chungking should Government move there, telCan 406, June
                    30, repeated Nanking 763.<note n="65" xml:id="d818fn65">
                        <hi rend="italic">Supra.</hi>
                    </note> French, Italian, Portuguese and Vatican representatives have received
                    definite instructions to do so. Britain anticipates following lead, but says
                    there is diversion in Nanking toward thought giving officer dual commission.
                    Australians and Philippines have no instructions. Netherlands situation is
                    complicated by recent transfer Counselor and ConGen to Hong Kong as ConGen to
                    fill vacancy there. Burmese, Turkish and Iranian representatives expect follow
                    our lead.</p>
                <p>Sent Dept Cantel 688, repeated Nanking 461.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clark</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
